## about Nuxt
Architecture
Nuxt is composed of different core packages:
Core Engine: nuxt
Bundlers: @nuxt/vite-builder and @nuxt/webpack-builder
Command line interface: nuxi
Server engine: nitro
Development kit: @nuxt/kit
